Description: Shoulder fragment of Aeolic bucchero large pottery vessel, perhaps a dinos or krater; incised inscription on the outside.
Curator's comments: Possibly from same vase as 1965,0930.415 and 1888,0601.621, which have similar strong vertical curvature.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GL.167)
